This topic describes how to install and configure Datadog Application Monitoring for VMware Tanzu.

##<a id='install'></a> Install and Configure Datadog Application Monitoring for VMware Tanzu

1. Download the product file for **Datadog Application Monitoring for VMware Tanzu** from the Tanzu Network.

2. Go to the Tanzu Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Import a Product** to upload the product file.

3. Select the product file downloaded in step **1**. This adds the tile to your staging area.

4. Click the newly added **Datadog Application Monitoring for VMware Tanzu** tile.

5. Enter your [Datadog API key](https://app.datadoghq.com/account/settings#api) in the **Datadog Config** section.

6. Click **Save**.

7. Return to the Tanzu Ops Manager Installation Dashboard and click **Apply changes** to install Datadog Application Monitoring for the VMware Tanzu tile.
